data.text:
Gang Name: Gambino Crime Family

Gang Leader(Owner of the in-game gang): Jake Gambino & Conor Gambino

Gang Leader Discord: Jaké#7747 & Corndog#4242

Summary of your gang (Backstory, etc): The Gambino Crime Family is a family of crime causing criminals started in Kamdan. Their terrors have moved to Florida, and we are actively committing multiple crimes like robbery, kidnapping, murder and etc. Our Family is our main priority, and we take care of each other first ALWAYS. We do not tolerate any kind of toxicity and we take our family very seriously. Our goal is to make Roleplay as fun as possible for everyone. We have gang uniforms and many others to come in the near future.

Why would you like to become official?: We would like to become official because we want to become a dedicated popular gang that can help roleplay further for civilians within the server. We also would like to become official because we are very serious and want our gang to succeed in the best way possible, With that being said I believe becoming an official gang will further help out the gang itself become stronger and larger.

Have you read the Official Gang Information thread, found here: Yes

Do you have a uniform available: Yes.
